{"tid":810991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"野生河狸被車撞重傷 還慘遭男子性侵亡","createTime":"2018-09-08T12:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T16:31:37.000Z","uid":38189,"like":123,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"294e6f47dffb4cca6ec781009aadabd4aaec84f7","tid":810991,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:14:59.000Z","msg":"美國一名男子遭控性侵河狸（beaver），週一遭當局逮捕，以虐待動物罪名起訴。<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓州肯納威克（Kennewick）一名女子行經哥倫比亞公園（Columbia Park），驚見一隻河狸被車撞傷。她趕緊跑回家拿箱子，準備帶河狸去給獸醫檢查。但她拿著箱子回到現場時，卻看見一名男子在河狸身旁。起初她以為男子是在安撫河狸，沒想到仔細一看，男子竟脫下褲子，身體壓在河狸上方。警方到場時，河狸已傷重身亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，他們接獲舉報，哥倫比亞公園一名男子與野生動物進行短暫性接觸。該男子是35歲的戴納（Richard Delp），以虐待動物及持有毒品安非他命等罪名被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻河狸一日入面遇到拉舒+泥清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db6fdef598c29a6c11e4b52f46aee991f8d6d61","tid":810991,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2d7c6b0236bc989c2da8760a806fa65c7335da","tid":810991,"uid":9231,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"屌完返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41edb7f8d1e3528b90598dc7a8295ac97bd1a14","tid":810991,"uid":4586,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"n bun<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623934ae1213e4d65c9c6a2d5d1361877f0df149","tid":810991,"uid":32816,"like":138,"dislike":0,"score":138,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"屌狸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e290b7f8e56f39436c581e98ca4b7dd30fbc80e","tid":810991,"uid":187682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"係咪真係咁渴求屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e321ac4efd4b7b33c3b9